WEBVTT

00:04:29.189 --> 00:04:30.439
The world will say to you,

00:04:30.463 --> 00:04:32.040
"We need to heal the planet."

00:04:32.995 --> 00:04:36.280
Start by saying, "No, thank you.
I don't need a plastic bag."

00:04:36.304 --> 00:04:38.348
Recycle, reuse.

00:04:38.372 --> 00:04:42.491
Start by picking up
one piece of trash on your block.

00:04:43.356 --> 00:04:44.973
The world will say to you,

00:04:45.581 --> 00:04:47.600
"There are too many problems."

00:04:48.415 --> 00:04:51.171
Do not be afraid
to be a part of the solutions.

00:04:51.865 --> 00:04:53.964
Start by discussing the issues.

00:04:54.364 --> 00:04:57.978
We cannot overcome what we ignore.

00:04:58.541 --> 00:05:00.501
The more we talk about things,